The death of Shaolin monk “Qiufeng” turns out to be a copy-and-paste script of the same pattern, and the hidden hand behind both points to the same person—agent Du Qiang. Follow that thread and it ultimately leads to the Chinese Communist Party’s red-elite families of Li Peng and Ye Ting. Is this still a coincidence, or a pre-designed playbook?
